        public org.springframework.web.servlet.ModelAndView updateRegisteredServiceEvaluationOrder(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                                                                                  javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response)
        Updates the RegisteredService.getEvaluationOrder(). Expects an id parameter to indicate the RegisteredService.getId() and the new evaluationOrder integer parameter from the request.
        Parameters:
        request - The request object that is expected to contain the id and evaluationOrder as parameters.
        response - The response object.
        Returns:
        a ModelAndView object back to the jsonView
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If either of the id or evaluationOrder are invalid or if the service cannot be located for that id by the active implementation of the ServicesManager.
